      "raw_text": "The new scale of the team drivers\nwent into effect this morning and has\nbeen signed by the Grimmer, Pacific\nand Spokane truck lines The Seahorn\nand Trowbridge people refused to. sign\nthe new scale and the union will re-\nquest the trades council to put these\ntwo firms on the unfair list at its next\nmeeting. The new scale calls for 1926\nper day, raise of % cents, and a\nscale of time and half for overtime."
